name: Vorax'Zhalethyr
automation:
  - type: condition
    condition: level < 10
    onTrue:
      - type: variable
        name: weapbonus
        value: "1"
    onFalse:
      - type: condition
        condition: level < 15
        onTrue:
          - type: variable
            name: weapbonus
            value: "2"
        onFalse:
          - type: variable
            name: weapbonus
            value: "3"
        errorBehaviour: "false"
    errorBehaviour: "false"

  - type: condition
    condition: choice == ""
    onTrue:
      - type: target
        target: all
        effects:
          - type: attack
            hit:
              - type: damage
                damage: 1d10 + {charismaMod} + {weapbonus} [slashing]
            miss: []  # Required field added to fix automation error
            attackBonus: charismaMod + proficiencyBonus + weapbonus
    onFalse: []
    errorBehaviour: "false"

  - type: condition
    condition: choice == "cleave"
    onTrue:
      - type: counter
        counter: Eldritch Cleave
        amount: "1"
        allowOverflow: false
      - type: target
        target: all
        effects:
          - type: save
            stat: wis
            fail:
              - type: damage
                damage: 3d6 [necrotic]
              - type: text
                text: Target is frightened until the end of its next turn.
                title: Dreadful Cleave
            success: []
            dc: 8 + charismaMod + proficiencyBonus + weapbonus
      - type: text
        title: Eldritch Cleave
        text: Once per short rest, when you hit with a melee attack, you can unleash an arc of necrotic force. Each creature of your choice within 10 feet must succeed a Wisdom saving throw or take 3d6 necrotic damage and become frightened until the end of its next turn.
    onFalse: []
    errorBehaviour: "false"

  - type: condition
    condition: choice == "glyph"
    onTrue:
      - type: text
        title: Glyphbound Spell
        text: Using your Scribes feature, you may inscribe a prepared 1st–3rd level spell into Vorax'Zhalethyr. You may cast the spell once without expending a spell slot. The spell uses Charisma as its casting ability, and the weapon acts as your focus.
    onFalse: []
    errorBehaviour: "false"

  - type: condition
    condition: choice == "siphon"
    onTrue:
      - type: counter
        counter: dummy
        amount: lastCounterRequestedAmount
        allowOverflow: false
      - type: variable
        name: x
        value: lastCounterRequestedAmount
      - type: counter
        counter:
          slot: x
        amount: "1"
        allowOverflow: false
        fixedValue: true
      - type: target
        target: self
        effects:
          - type: temphp
            amount: 5*{x}
          - type: text
            text: You draw magic into your blade, gaining {5*x} temp HP.
            title: Arcane Siphon
    onFalse: []
    errorBehaviour: "false"

  - type: condition
    condition: choice == "surge"
    onTrue:
      - type: roll
        dice: 1d20
        name: surge
        hidden: false
        displayName: Arcane Instability
      - type: condition
        condition: surge <= 2
        onTrue:
          - type: target
            target: self
            effects:
              - type: damage
                damage: 2d10 [psychic]
              - type: text
                title: Echo Surge!
                text: A surge of unstable power lashes back. You take 2d10 psychic damage, and the spell slot is lost.
        onFalse:
          - type: text
            title: Spell Held Stable
            text: The arcane energies stabilize. No backlash occurs.
    onFalse: []
    errorBehaviour: "false"

  - type: text
    title: Lore
    text: >-
      Once the quill of a long-dead scribe who delved too deep into the Astral Echoes, Vorax'Zhalethyr was reforged into a scythe by a pact-wielder seeking power both ancient and personal. Its edge carves not only flesh, but memory.

  - type: text
    title: Features
    text: >-
      **Hexblade Weapon:** Counts as a pact weapon. You may use Charisma for attack and damage rolls.

      **Eldritch Cleave:** Once per short or long rest, hit with a melee attack to force nearby creatures (10 ft) to make a DC (8 + Cha mod + prof) Wisdom save or take 3d6 necrotic damage and become frightened until the end of their next turn.

      **Glyphbound Spell:** You may inscribe one 1st–3rd level prepared Wizard spell into the weapon using your Order of Scribes feature. It may be cast once using Charisma without a spell slot.

      **Arcane Siphon:** As a bonus action, expend a spell slot to gain temporary HP equal to 5 × the slot level.

      **Echo Surge (Curse):** When casting a spell through the blade, roll 1d20. On a 1–2, the spell slot is lost and you take 2d10 psychic damage.

  - type: condition
    condition: choice == "help"
    onTrue:
      - type: text
        title: Help
        text: >-
          - Melee Attack: `-choice`  
          - Eldritch Cleave: `-choice cleave`  
          - Glyphbound Spell: `-choice glyph`  
          - Arcane Siphon (with -amt slot level): `-choice siphon -amt 2`  
          - Echo Surge (before casting spell): `-choice surge`
    onFalse: []
    errorBehaviour: "false"

_v: 2
proper: true
